TextParameterSet.text: Unlimited Projects...
Flash'iteasy lets you create, duplicate and edit any type of project : websites, banners, keynotes, animations... where objects can be shared between projects.
Unlimited Designs...
With no mandatory template system, Flash'Iteasy entitles your designers to work in a familiar environment and generate interactive sketches at short notice
Use as many pages as you need, regardless of the complexity required by your tree-structure. Page sizes can vary during navigation, so you can change user-experiences with a single click.
Unlimited Structure...
Unlimited Creation...
Use your own specifics font types, animate your contents, design and mix masks, filters and effects, all without a single line of code.
Unlimited Development...
While Flash'Iteasy framework is open-source, you can always participate by creating and bringing new milestones to the project. Join the community !
Unlimited Extensibility...
If Flash'Iteasy doesn't provide what you need, you can! Flash'Iteasy boosts your coders with a global framework entitling complex objects to be added and managed at run-time.

Flash'Iteasy takes care of most rebarbative tasks, entitling designers, coders and editors to concentrate on their task, regardless of technology.

Use the power!
Easier, quicker, gains time and value
Rich content creation & management

Compose images, filters, layers, effects and masks. Use your very own fonts. Design pages of different sizes. Animate anything anytime.

Get creative!
Open and evolutive professional tools

Design entire websites in days. Present interactive drafts in hours. Take advantage of unlimited visual creation or extend Flash'Iteasy's code.
